---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Leadership Growth Consulting | Systems, AI, and Structure for Business Owners">
  <Nav />

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-white pt-28 pb-24 lg:pt-36 lg:pb-32">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-brand uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-semibold mb-8">
        Leadership Growth Consulting
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl lg:text-7xl text-zinc-900 leading-[1.1] mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Most owners are the engine. The goal is to become the architect.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-500 max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        I work with business owners to build the systems, AI workflows, and team structure
        that let them step back, without the business going quiet.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-5">
        <a
          href="https://calendly.com/will-leadershipgrowthconsulting/30min"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block bg-brand text-white px-8 py-4 font-medium text-base hover:bg-brand-hover transition-colors duration-200"
        >
          Book a discovery call
        </a>
        <span class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">No pitch. Just a conversation.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-zinc-900 mb-8">Sound familiar?</h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-lg text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        <p>You built something real. A proper business, real clients, a team (or the start of one).</p>
        <p>
          But somewhere along the way, you became the thing holding it all together.
          You are still closing most of the sales. Still the first call when something goes wrong.
          Still the one making decisions that probably do not need you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-900 font-medium">The business runs because you do.</p>
        <p>
          And while you are heads-down running it, everything else gets pushed: more time with family,
          staying active, actually thinking clearly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-zinc-900 font-medium">
          You are not failing. You are just still in the middle of everything.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHO IT'S FOR -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-zinc-900 mb-10">This is for you if...</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-12">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-lg text-zinc-600">
            <svg class="text-brand mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            You run a business with 5 to 20 people
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-lg text-zinc-600">
            <svg class="text-brand mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            Profitable, but you are the bottleneck
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-lg text-zinc-600">
            <svg class="text-brand mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            The business relies on you too heavily for decisions, firefighting, and keeping things moving
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-lg text-zinc-600">
            <svg class="text-brand mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            You want to hire the right people and actually trust them
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-lg text-zinc-600">
            <svg class="text-brand mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            You have a life outside work that you would actually like to live
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4 text-lg text-zinc-600">
            <svg class="text-brand mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
              <path d="M3 8L6.5 11.5L13 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            You are not looking for hype, a new framework, or someone who disappears after the strategy deck
          </li>
        </ul>
        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-brand pl-6 text-lg text-zinc-600 italic leading-relaxed">
          If you are running a good business but spending all your time inside it instead of on top of it,
          you are in the right place.
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT CHANGES -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-zinc-900 mb-4">
          What we actually work on
        </h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-500 text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Leadership challenges met with practical solutions. Systems, tools, and AI workflows
          that take the operational weight off your shoulders.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-zinc-200">
        <div class="bg-white p-8">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">Build systems that save you hours</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            AI workflows, automation, and process design applied to the parts of your business
            where you are doing things you should not be. Real hours back, not added complexity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">Hire properly</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Build the role, find the right person, onboard them so they can actually do the job.
            Not just "hire someone and hope for the best."
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">Get problems off your desk</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Stop being the first call when something goes wrong. Build the structure, document
            the decisions, and trust the team to handle what should not need you.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">Know where your time should go</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Work out what only you can do, and stop doing everything else. Clearer priorities,
            better decisions, less firefighting.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">Step back without things going quiet</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Build a business that does not need you for everything. Then actually step back: family,
            sport, thinking time, without the guilt or the anxiety that it will fall apart.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FREE RESOURCE -->
  <section class="bg-[#1D3A2B] py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-white mb-4">
        See what we could build for your business
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Get a free report showing the specific systems, automations, and AI workflows
        that would save you hours every week and make your operations run smoother.
      </p>
      <a
        href="mailto:will@leadershipgrowthconsulting.com?subject=Free%20Efficiency%20Report&body=Hi%20Will%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20receive%20the%20free%20efficiency%20report.%20Here%27s%20a%20bit%20about%20my%20business%3A"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-zinc-900 px-8 py-4 font-medium text-base hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        Get your free report
      </a>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-sm mt-4">No obligation. Just a practical look at where AI and systems can help.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-zinc-900 mb-14">How we work together</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">01</p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">Understand the real situation</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            We start with a discovery call to understand where you are, what is actually getting
            in the way, and whether working together makes sense. If it does, we go deeper in
            a strategy session.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">02</p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">Build what is missing</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            We get into the business together. I help you build the sales system, the hiring
            process, the team structure, the AI workflows, whatever it is that is keeping you
            stuck in the middle.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-brand text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">03</p>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-zinc-900 mb-3">You step back (properly)</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            With the right structure in place, you stop being the bottleneck. You spend more
            time on what actually grows the business, and more time on the rest of your life.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-14 text-zinc-500 italic border-l-4 border-zinc-200 pl-6 max-w-2xl text-base">
        This is not a course or a coaching programme you do alongside running your business.
        It is proper work, done together, inside your actual business.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section class="bg-stone-50 py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-zinc-900 mb-2">8+</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Years working alongside business owners</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-zinc-900 mb-2">7 figures</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Owners supported to exit at multiple 7-figure valuations</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-zinc-900 mb-2">1,000s</p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Hours saved through systems, AI, and process design</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLIENT STORY -->
  <section class="bg-[#1D3A2B] py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-semibold mb-10">
        What it looks like in practice
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-lg text-white/85 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I started working with one client back in 2020, just before Covid hit. He was a one-man band:
          a desk in a coworking space above a library, revenue around £100k, everything running through him.
        </p>
        <p>
          Six years on, he is at £3 million. He has a team. He takes the school holidays off with his kids.
          He pays his people well and goes home in time for what matters.
        </p>
        <p>
          He built that. But I was alongside him every step of the way. Through the uncertainty, the hard
          decisions, the moments it felt like a lot. We built his team structure together, wrote job
          descriptions, set up proper onboarding, and worked out what he should keep doing versus what he
          should hand off. We put the systems in place that took the weight off.
        </p>
        <p>
          His week now splits between work and sport, a bit like a school timetable. He is still growing,
          still on the front foot, still building new service lines. But he does it from a position of
          choice, not obligation. He spends his time on what he is genuinely best at: the thinking, the
          vision, the ideas. And he is around for the things that matter outside of it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        href="/results"
        class="inline-block mt-12 text-emerald-400 text-sm font-medium hover:text-white transition-colors"
      >
        Read more about how it works <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT WILL -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="order-last lg:order-first">
          <p class="text-brand uppercase tracking-widest text-xs font-semibold mb-8">A bit about me</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              I have spent years building and leading sales teams, developing senior leaders,
              and working inside businesses to fix what was not working. I have done the executive
              coaching side too. But what I found is that most business owners do not need more
              coaching. They need someone alongside them to help drive things when it gets hard
              or lonely, and to actually build what is missing.
            </p>
            <p>
              So that is what I do. I work alongside business owners to put the systems, the AI
              workflows, and the team structure in place that lets them step back, without things
              falling apart.
            </p>
            <p>
              I am based in Surrey. My honest ambition outside the work is pretty simple: quality time
              with family, a business that genuinely helps people, and more rounds of golf with friends.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/about"
            class="inline-block mt-8 text-brand text-sm font-medium hover:text-brand-hover transition-colors"
          >
            More about me <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="order-first lg:order-last">
          <img
            src="/images/will.jpg"
            alt="Will Harvey"
            width="600"
            height="750"
            loading="lazy"
            class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover object-top grayscale"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FINAL CTA -->
  <section class="bg-zinc-900 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white mb-6">Ready to talk?</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg mb-3 leading-relaxed">
        Book a discovery call. It is a conversation, not a pitch. We will talk about where you are,
        what is getting in the way, and what a different version of your week could look like.
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg mb-10 leading-relaxed">
        If it makes sense to work together, we will go from there. If it does not, you will still
        leave with something useful.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://calendly.com/will-leadershipgrowthconsulting/30min"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-zinc-900 px-8 py-4 font-medium text-base hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        Book a discovery call
      </a>
      <p class="text-zinc-600 text-sm mt-6">
        I typically work with 4-6 business owners at a time. Worth reaching out sooner rather than later.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
